{"tid":1568949,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可令運動可持續？　拋磚引玉，歡迎討論，不喜就屌","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T23:37:54.000Z","uid":90941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"959f5f77b45bbcb0172cbf6b43b6c657ad4bcc4a","tid":1568949,"uid":90941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong>大家抗爭左超過三個月，呢家政府只係將徹回修例，其他四項仍然遙遙無期，其實大家都預左會無限期抗爭<br />\n<br />\n但究竟點先可以持續，將抗爭面擴大至政府同建制內部崩潰？令抗爭者越來越強大？<br />\n<br />\n先講最低難度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復各區連儂牆</span>，一星期貼一次又好兩次又好，唔好俾佢地停，將抗爭帶入社區，有人撕或燒就由佢，繼續撕一貼十，堅持下去<br />\n<br />\n二﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貼牆日順便齊齊唱榮光</span>，中英文都要唱，港歌黎，大家有共鳴更團結，互相鼓勵士氣<br />\n<br />\n三﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼續搞人鏈，遊行係表態，人鏈卻係和理非做更多既 baby step</span>，試左呢步先，之後有勇氣出更多力<br />\n<br />\n四﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Keep 住行出黎</span>，唔好因為警暴同黑社會而怕，擔心就搵多幾個朋友，只要人多黑狗就唔敢亂黎<br />\n<br />\n五﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有圖出圖</span>，對自己友或懶係中間派 &mdash; 鼓勵佢地出多啲黎做多啲野﹗<span style=\"color: red;\">對大陸人 &mdash; 提醒下佢地自己有毒奶粉地溝油假疫苗﹗</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">對犬黑 &mdash; 分化為主，中共遲早攞黎祭旗換民望，甚至收丁權都無人可憐﹗</span><br />\n<br />\n六﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有錢出錢</span>，有錢要捐錢，612 星火唔使講<br />\n<br />\n七﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有技教技</span>，有唔少抗爭者經過呢一波會好艱難，搵食都唔知點搵，大家幫手教，甚至幫手搵份工，例如三行之類，巴絲有難，互相扶持﹗<br />\n<br />\n八﹒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫襯自己友</span>，平日甚至 Buy Bye Day 都只幫襯撐我地既人</strong><br />\n<br />\n最普通一粒星既寫住咁多先<br />\n<br />\n最後幾句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n巴絲有難，相互扶持<br />\n不割蓆，不批評，不篤灰，齊檢討<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港﹗﹗﹗<br />\nMay Glory be to Hong Kong!!!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"07593fce5c11c8f21e0ce0200a433f2dd911a132","tid":1568949,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85d923c446419ff256ff5c0210a78defadba7cc9","tid":1568949,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 係對家濫捕唔係我地送頭 仲要警覺休班狗同民鬥民問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568901</a>"},{"pid":"c809b4c646d44b8ac626f0bd1bb7b4ab62efaf0c","tid":1568949,"uid":282508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n915 東角道見﹗"},{"pid":"84cabd5d28a6fec459e71d04a16d442500df3a3a","tid":1568949,"uid":282508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"7a413ae06404e61e56b6b157617c763c67cadc1b","tid":1568949,"uid":91218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed582a2996710c5a4415e4c57c741c64280fa847","tid":1568949,"uid":61101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 係對家濫捕唔係我地送頭 仲要警覺休班狗同民鬥民問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568901\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568901</a><br />\n你推我又推"},{"pid":"426ae440e5af36d3c1638402bd598680ea093f82","tid":1568949,"uid":282508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T23:37:54.000Z","msg":"推 2/10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl